77 SUNSET STRIP 

24. Hong Kong Caper  3/20/1959
Jeff Spencer takes off for Hong Kong when a note from an army pilot puts him on the trail of a woman named Candy and a fortune in diamonds.
  Writer: Steve Fisher
Director: George Waggner
Guest star: Karen Steele (Candy Varga), Neil Hamilton   (Ned Shelby), Weaver Levy (Sam Fong), Frank Wilcox (Paul Nolan, Sr.), Reggie Nalder (Run Run Lee), Willard Waterman (George Wells), Kathleen Freeman (Hannah Wells)

25. A Check Will Do Nicely    3/27/1959  
Stu Bailey is hired to go to Paris to rescue a kidnapped American schoolgirl and save a valuable painting.
  Writer: Dwight Taylor, Alan Caillou
Director: Ida Lupino
Guest star: Roger Til (Antoin Bonhomme), Danielle Aubry (Suzette), Florence Marly (Madeleine), Edward Platt (Mr. Jacobin), Robin Hughes (Sandby), Janet Lake (Laura Jacobin), Louis Mercier (Robert), Rolfe Sedan (Tissot)
